# The Backstage sample is a standalone, yarn-managed app outside the pnpm workspace (eslint skips
# `other-examples/**` for the same reason). Its package.json sets `"prettier":
# "@backstage/cli/config/prettier"`, so prettier tries to load that config and dies — `Cannot find
# package '@backstage/cli'` — because a root `pnpm install` never installs its dependencies. It also
# vendors a 3 MB `.yarn/releases/*.cjs` that we have no business reformatting. Its own toolchain
# formats it. The other samples have no prettier config of their own, so they stay formatted here.
other-examples/backstage-with-unleash/

